Fortifications
--------------

Structures which may aid fighters in battle are rated for
their defensive bonus.

	Castle Imperius [gx56], castle, defense 25

During battle, the fortification rating is added to the defense
number for each of the men inside the structure.

The structure may take hits during the battle, reducing its
defensive rating.  Once the defense rating reaches zero,
further hits may cause the building to become damaged.
A fully damaged building (100% damage) will collapse, ejecting
its occupants.


